{
  "stem": "9156.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where is the young lady?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I was wondering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you have nothing to--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She has nothing to sit on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There are lots of-- lots of pillows.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why don't you take a pillow?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Really?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can put that over?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That would be nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gisela Konopka.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "G-I-S-E-L-A, and the last one is K-O-N-O-P-K-A.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But all my friends call me Gisa, G-I-S-A.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Berlin, Germany.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mendel Peiper and Bronia Peiper, born Buttermann.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, that I have to spell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Peiper is spelled P-E-I-P-E-R.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mendel.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "M-E-N-D-E-L.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother's name is Bronia, B-R-O-N-I-A.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the last name is Buttermann, B-U-T-T-E-R-M-A-N-N.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But sometimes it's spelled Pitterman, P-I-T-T-E-R, and the rest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the kind of papers they got.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- they were immigrants from, at that time, Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's today, Poland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And certainly, the papers were not always kept exact.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when you talk earliest, I was born in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a large building.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember very vividly the outbreak of World War I.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was a little kid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I wasn't even four years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we had a little store, and there was a person that lived in that same building.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[TELEPHONE RINGING]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My first memory-- I mean, there are other small ones-- but very important was the outbreak of World War I, and that's about 1914.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a small store, and somebody came from upstairs, somebody we called uncle, but he was not an uncle.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he yelled the word, mobilmachung, M-O-B-I-L-M-A-C-H-U-N-G.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the word.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It means, there's a war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I saw my mother crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I saw my father getting very white in the face.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- and then it goes on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I could tell a lot of memories about that.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
